Once upon a time, there was an infamous and loadmouthed astronaut named Melvin.
It starts aboard a space station orbiting a mountainous planet.
Melvin and his friend Roddy chart their flight path to this mountainous planet.
Melvin and his friend Roddy went to another planet to find a magic rock. 
The magic rock teleported them to deadly planet.
Melvin and Roddy both died.
The end.
